text: Reino Tuominen (30 March 1935 - 27 December 1974) was a Finnish wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman bantamweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:1974 deaths Category:Finnish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Finland Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Kotka
